| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1323 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 166f9aa8-4fa9-58eb-ae38-eca14f2a87a0"
